data.description: Location, Location, Location !Move In Ready. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home has been freshly painted through-out. All new flooring and carpet. Also features a large family room and living room that can also be used as a dining area. Large front porch. Enclosed back porch with attached deck. This home is located on a large corner lot. Lots of storage on the main level and in the basement. One car detached garage. Nothing to do but move in. This home has character and charm. Miles form Bridge St and the Harbor.
